{"about_the_game":"Glow is a fast-paced action game in the spirit of the good old 80's &amp; 90's 2D top-down shooters, presented in modern 3D graphics. You control a lone but brave Firefly, to help her fight evil spiders and critters that try to hunt you down.<br><br>But fear not, dying is not the end. The more you play, the more perks you can collect for your flying hero, which help you to get rid of even more enemies. Are you good enough to lead the global online leaderboard and become Glow world champion?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GAMEPLAY</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Control your Firefly in a fast-paced action game with a zoomable 3rd person view<br></li><li> Various types of Spiders and anti-aircraft Slugs try to shoot you down<br></li><li> Equip the Firefly with various weapons, ordnance &amp; passive abilities (500+ combinations)<br></li><li> Collect power-ups to heal, gain more points, or even spawn Minions that fight on your side<br></li><li> Increase your score by killing enemies to unlock new perks and climb up the leaderboard<br></li><li> Easy to learn, hard to master: Just play and become better over time</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Blood","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/491830/5a2dec29c2f96be00f785df89bb42f88aef6fe91.jpg"},{"name":"Spider Nuisance","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/491830/ccaaa02dfca0c54529866776a39043e2c006d7a2.jpg"},{"name":"Spider Menace","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/491830/6b2567fa2bc00858cbee4bad7438d77befb3fe0b.jpg"},{"name":"Spider Killer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/491830/722e4783871a8f5dade7c5127168062d17b621ab.jpg"},{"name":"Spider Nemesis","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/491830/5e66a87d932fc059bac4a653fcbd7a2c1069c00b.jpg"},{"name":"Scorge of Arachnoids","path":"https://cdn.